@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xlhgsf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.abs((v1 - wp.abs(v2 + 0.38)))
    v2 = wp.sin(v0)
    v0 = wp.cos(tmp)
    v0 = (wp.exp(wp.cos(v0 + 0.76)) - (0.06 - (tmp + 0.92 + v2 + 0.90)))
    v2 = (v2 / wp.sin(v0))
    v1 = v1
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.exp(wp.cos(v1 + 0.52)))
    v2 = 0.53
    data[tid] = v0
